Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.80,script,,0,0,0,,Hey Daddy, will there be a panda? A panda?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.60,script,,0,0,0,,What? panda?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:00.80,script,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.10,script,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.10,script,,0,0,0,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:01.90,script,,0,0,0,,Brother, if you have nothing to do, could you at least clean the bathtub?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:03.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she notice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.30,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was only for an instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.80,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.30,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.90,script,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.70,script,,0,0,0,,What should we have for lunch? Is soumen okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.70,tlnote,,0,0,0,,{\a6}soumen = cold white noodles, eaten at summer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:23.40,script,,0,0,0,,Dad hasn't come back since he left to get his hair cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.20,script,,0,0,0,,Let's just go ahead and eat-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.00,script,,0,0,0,,You went into my room, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.60,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.60,script,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the day to take out the trash, so earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.70,script,,0,0,0,,I've told you before, haven't I? Not to go in without my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.70,script,,0,0,0,,But... all I did was empty your waste basket. I didn't touch anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.40,script,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:53.50,script,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that I'll take care of my own trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:57.30,script,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't like it if I went into your room right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.70,script,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.60,script,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:08.30,script,,0,0,0,,Idiot. You're just too inconsiderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.00,script,,0,0,0,,You don't have to put it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.90,script,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.70,script,,0,0,0,,It's unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.60,script,,0,0,0,,Don't ever make me repeat myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.70,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.90,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Insinuation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:41.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. No way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was just for an instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.50,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way she could have noticed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.10,script,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.90,script,,0,0,0,,That's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.30,script,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:24.80,script,,0,0,0,,Definitely suspicious. Why would he get so angry for just going into his room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.80,script,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was something he really didn't want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.60,script,,0,0,0,,Ah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.40,script,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.60,script,,0,0,0,,A present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.30,script,,0,0,0,,He makes himself seem like a major jerk,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:38.00,script,,0,0,0,,and tomorrow he'll suddenly transform into the nice big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.60,script,,0,0,0,,Ah! That kind of a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.00,script,,0,0,0,,Nanoka, it's your birthday tomorrow right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:53.50,script,,0,0,0,,No way! No way! That's definitely not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.70,script,,0,0,0,,Maybe Nanoka's big brother is pretty simple minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.40,script,,0,0,0,,That's not a bamboo tree anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.10,script,,0,0,0,,It is the Tanabata Rendezvous Party.
