Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.40,script,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.40,script,,0,0,0,,Sure! I was just about to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.80,script,,0,0,0,,Is it all right not to call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:47.10,script,,0,0,0,,After Nanoka-chan came, you've been calling home every time you're going to be late, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.00,script,,0,0,0,,No I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.30,script,,0,0,0,,There's no use hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.90,script,,0,0,0,,Why don't you wipe your mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.80,script,,0,0,0,,I don't care about her.
