Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:42.70,script,,0,0,0,,I have to go out early tomorrow too, so I won't need a lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just say it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.10,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I'm sorry I sniffed it.{\i0}
