Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.90,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nanoka its your birthday tomorrow right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:15.00,script,,0,0,0,,Your father called.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:20.70,script,,0,0,0,,Nanoka chan left without taking an umbrella, so he asked you to wait for her at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.90,script,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.20,script,,0,0,0,,He can't leave because he's preparing her birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.40,script,,0,0,0,,Birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.40,script,,0,0,0,,This is why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.40,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.40,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you know what day it is tomorrow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:48.00,script,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go for her? I don't mind if you leave early--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.50,script,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.40,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my chance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to use her birthday to fix everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.50,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can say "Congratulations!" or "I'm sorry I forgot about it!" and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:16.70,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bring up all these plans and make her happy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:21.70,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a birthday idiot, so if I give her some flowers or something she'll probably cry and thank me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:29.80,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This way I can get rid of my guilt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.60,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can probably...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.40,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.80,script,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.80,script,,0,0,0,,No... No! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.70,script,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do! I'm the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.40,script,,0,0,0,,God I'm the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:18.40,script,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.50,script,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I forgot about your birthday... And I wanted to say sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.80,script,,0,0,0,,There's no deeper meaning in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:23.90,script,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:30.80,script,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.80,script,,0,0,0,,Did you come to get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.90,script,,0,0,0,,No this isn't for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.60,script,,0,0,0,,Is that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.30,script,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't... It's for the Buddha idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.40,script,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:02.20,script,,0,0,0,,I thought you were really mad at me because I saw you naked in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.60,script,,0,0,0,,Why would I get mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:19.10,script,,0,0,0,,It's normal to be just in my underwear the whole day with this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.40,script,,0,0,0,,Eh? It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.40,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:28.40,script,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.00,script,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:50.80,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You were really scary last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.30,script,,0,0,0,,For your birthday present,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.40,script,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.50,script,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.20,script,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.40,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was supposed to be able to do it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:25.70,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To get rid... of my guilt...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:38.70,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:18.95,script,,0,0,0,,I'll say it however many times as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:21.41,script,,0,0,0,,I innocently really want a teenage younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:23.82,script,,0,0,0,,Is that a crime? Is it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.97,0:23:26.41,script,,0,0,0,,Then as we're fighting over the TV channels, our love will sprout...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.40,script,,0,0,0,,Whipping punishment!
